  [Permalink: uncompile](https://github.com/zdharma-continuum/zinit#uncompile)
  
  List plugins that are compiled.
  
  ```
  zinit [options] uncompile PLUGIN
  ```
  
  | Option | Description |
  | --- | --- |
  | `-a, --all` | Remove any compiled files for all plugins |
