  # Tuning My Terminal: How Zinit Made My Zsh Setup Fast, Flexible, and Actually Fun
  
  ## A modern Zsh setup with Zinit, Rust tools, and Starship — built for speed, clarity, and a terminal that feels _yours_.
  
  [![Smyekh](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:32:32/1*ZxiMDvzHRgoqyffqOc75_Q.png)](https://medium.com/@Smyekh?source=post_page---byline--5f6450589003---------------------------------------)
  
